  Version Bump to 2.7.4.

  14 Feb 2009; Alistair Bush <ali_bush@gentoo.org> scala-2.7.3-r1.ebuild:
  Add block on scala-bin. see #247401.

  14 Feb 2009; Alistair Bush <ali_bush@gentoo.org> scala-2.7.3-r1.ebuild:
  Adding PDEPEND on app-emacs/scala-mode. Thanks go to ulm.

